**Basic C Aptitude Questions:**

**1. What is the output of the following C code?**

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int a = 5, b = 10;
    a = a + b;
    b = a - b;
    a = a - b;
    printf("%d %d", a, b);
    return 0;
}
```

